    {
      "id": "18b4750c-f3ba-802a-b797-d779de924b2a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There are enormous conomic benefits to draw from automating course-selection and many current predictive models actually try to predict the number of students that may enroll in a given course. Multiple issues exist with this approach:",
