    {
      "id": "18b4750c-f3ba-8005-8c81-fa78fdb6f49b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, authors propose a recommender system for courses only using information available in the School’s institutional system. The approach starts with the extraction of features and their use with Analytical Hierarchy Process to predict course selections. Tests done on a sample of 1061 higher education students.",
